abstract: Around 35 African migrants are among top prize winners in Spain's Christmas lottery; winners include Senegalese man who told media he and his wife were rescued by Spain's coast guard in 2007.
lead_paragraph: About 35 migrants are among the top prize winners of Spain’s Christmas lottery, according to the owner of a lottery agency.

headline.main: Spain: A Change in Fortunes for African Migrants
